name: Parser.Test

values.name: run
values.comment:
Check if a parser is backtrackable or not.

    run (keyword "import") "imp"
    --> (Err _, True)

    run (keyword "import") "import"
    --> (Ok (), False)

    run spaces "  "
    --> (Ok (), False)

    run (backtrackable spaces) "  "
    --> (Ok (), True)
values.type: Parser.Parser a -> String.String -> ( Result.Result (List.List Parser.DeadEnd) a, Basics.Bool )
